{
  "stem": "5388.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And oh, hey, how about some money for the-- for the defense forces of Poland?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Father, of course, contributed too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I remember my elder sister, Pola, the one that was killed, she was going to a Polish gymnasium-- gymnasium, which was-- no-- Jewish girls weren't accepted so easily.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were maybe four or five all, but she was an excellent student, at  top.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- not in Raczki.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was going in Suwalki.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no gymnasium in-- in Raczki.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Raczki just had the grade-- grammar school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she was-- she used to come with friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember once her school had an outing and they came, stopped at our house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Mother was feeding them, and there was all those young girls-- food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was all Polish girls.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were just maybe three, four Jewish girls, and my sister among them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were on an outing to the border in the woods, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that was an example of Jews and Poles--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--were-- did seem to get along.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know many-- I-- I see-- you know, I hear it many time, anti-Semitism and other stuff.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- in Raczki, I did not feel it on my bones.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Never did, in Raczki.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember that they used to come pick me up from school, as I told you about it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that was because supposedly trouble, and there was in-- some agitation about not to buy a Jew's.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now it's already coming, '37, '38, the influence of Hitler in Germany is most probably must have been-- already came in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it's a small town, you know, where everybody knew one another.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
